  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summary</h2>Play as a cleaning robot, as you vacuum a variety of unique environments. Whilst listening to a relaxing soundtrack, in this fun and casual simulator.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/e1b7f9ae032a75a5e640c8f803b799f4.poster.avif?t=1636406330\" width=600 height=234 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/e1b7f9ae032a75a5e640c8f803b799f4.webm?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/e1b7f9ae032a75a5e640c8f803b799f4.mp4?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2>'Robo Vacuum Simulator' is a relaxing game in which you immerse yourself as a cleaning robot. You will vacuum a variety of environments, including houses, hospitals, office spaces, garages, attics(who puts a cleaning robot in the attic?) and more...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Levels</h2>Vacuum rubbish in unique environments:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/ec7d777fab903fae1275bb5ca49ca067.poster.avif?t=1636406330\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/ec7d777fab903fae1275bb5ca49ca067.webm?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/ec7d777fab903fae1275bb5ca49ca067.mp4?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/28c3c9cbe9858785f006b66196b2f145.poster.avif?t=1636406330\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/28c3c9cbe9858785f006b66196b2f145.webm?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/28c3c9cbe9858785f006b66196b2f145.mp4?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/4358c77b8d050d7d8697b855f371e5d4.poster.avif?t=1636406330\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/4358c77b8d050d7d8697b855f371e5d4.webm?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/4358c77b8d050d7d8697b855f371e5d4.mp4?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/5b2a6029784964be2fa9de0ebec9ab55.poster.avif?t=1636406330\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/5b2a6029784964be2fa9de0ebec9ab55.webm?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1766150/extras/5b2a6029784964be2fa9de0ebec9ab55.mp4?t=1636406330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Find and vacuum up rubbish<br><br></li><li>Remember to recharge at the charging dock when low on battery<br><br></li><li>Return to the charging dock when all rubbish is vacuumed.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop p